(44, 20, 4, 49, 6, 21, 21, 'Tychicus', 'Connection of Tychicus in Scripture', 'This connection highlights the presence of Tychicus in both passages. In Acts 20:4, Tychicus is mentioned as a companion of Paul, while Ephesians 6:21 identifies him as a beloved brother and minister.', 'keyword', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 4, 55, 4, 20, 20, 'Trophimus', 'Connection of Trophimus in Acts and Timothy', 'Both passages emphasize Trophimus, linking his presence in Acts with his later mention in Timothy. This connection highlights the continuity of Trophimus''s journey and circumstances in Paul''s ministry.', 'keyword', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 20, 4, 44, 16, 1, 1, 'Timotheus', 'Connection of Timothy''s Role', 'Both passages emphasize Timothy''s presence in Paul''s ministry. In Acts 16:1, Timothy is introduced as a disciple, while in Acts 20:4, he is mentioned as a companion of Paul on his journey.', 'parallel', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
