(44, 20, 4, 55, 4, 12, 12, 'Tychicus', 'Connection of Tychicus in Scripture', 'This connection highlights the presence of Tychicus in both passages. In Acts 20:4, Tychicus is mentioned as a companion of Paul, while in 2 Timothy 4:12, he is noted as being sent to Ephesus.', 'keyword', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
