(44, 20, 18, 47, 1, 12, 12, 'what manner I have been with you', 'Sincerity in Conduct', 'Both passages emphasize the manner of conduct in ministry. Acts 20:18 speaks of how Paul was with the believers, while 2 Corinthians 1:12 highlights the sincerity and simplicity of their conversation.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
