(44, 20, 19, 47, 4, 7, 11, 'temptations', 'Endurance in Suffering', 'Both passages emphasize the experience of suffering and perseverance in the face of trials. Acts 20:19 mentions ''temptations'' and ''tears,'' while 2 Corinthians 4:7-11 describes being ''troubled,'' ''persecuted,'' and ''cast down,'' yet remaining resilient.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
